Cookies When you’re craving cookies, make sure you have some on hand. Amazon.com offers a wide range of cookies, including shortbread, oatmeal, peanut butter, chocolate chip, sugar, gluten-free, sandwich cookies, and variety packs. If you can’t resist the creamy center inside of an Oreo, we have several flavors to choose from. If you’re looking for a certain type of Milano or a favorite Kashi cookie, we have those, too. Prefer something simpler? Try our butter cookies, biscotti, or fortune cookies. Let Amazon.com help you satisfy your sweet tooth.





